title: Two Sides to Every Date: The Puzzle Debacle
description: Brian has been dating Mallory for a couple of months and just went to her family cabin last weekend.  They seemed to be doing good but on Tuesday she started giving him the cold shoulder.  We call Mallory to see why she's not talking to Brian much anymore.
